%header#landing_header.bg-image-full.py-5.min-100.mb-0.landing-image-1

%section#what.py-5
  .container
    %h1 What is the BAR-U-EAT #CarFreeChallenge?
    %p
      The pursuit of adventure sports often involves travel, but
      we're here to let you know that there's adventure just steps beyond your front door!
    %p
      With the climate quickly changing and altering the way we live and play, there's
      no better way to preserve our fun and protect our planet than stepping outside and
      taking advantage of the area you live in!
    %p
      So join us in pledging to minimize the carbon impact of our recreation by finding
      adventures close to home and leaving your car parked!
    %p
      = link_to 'Sign up', new_user_registration_path
      and set your own #CarFreeChallenge goals today!

%section.py-5.bg-image-full.landing-image-2
  &nbsp;

%section#who.py-5
  .container
    %h1 Who's participating?
    .container
      .row
        .col-md-12
          .card
            .card-header Leaderboard
            .card-body
              = render partial: 'home/leaderboard'
        .col-md-12
          .card
            .card-header #CarFreeChallenge Participants
            .card-body.text-center.p-0
              %h1
                .badge.text-primary= @summary[:users]
            %hr.my-0
            .card-header
              Emissions Avoided
              = surround "(", ")" do
                %a{ href: "#", data: { toggle: "tooltip" }, title: "The average passenger vehicle emits 404 grams per mile." } ?
            .card-body.text-center
              %h1
                .badge.text-primary= emissions_given_distance(@summary[:distance_sum])
            %hr.my-0
            .card-header Vertical Gain (feet)
            .card-body.text-center.p-0
              %h1
                .badge.text-primary #{number_with_delimiter(@summary[:vertical_gain_sum].to_i)} / #{number_with_delimiter(@summary[:vertical_gain_goal].to_i)}
            %hr.my-0
            .card-body.bg-primary.text-white
              .progress
                .progress-bar.bg-secondary{ style: "width: #{@summary[:vertical_gain_sum] * 100 / @summary[:vertical_gain_goal]}%;" }
            %hr.my-0
            .card-header Distance (miles)
            .card-body.text-center.p-0
              %h1
                .badge.text-primary #{number_with_delimiter(@summary[:distance_sum].to_i)} / #{number_with_delimiter(@summary[:distance_goal].to_i)}
            %hr.my-0
            .card-body.bg-primary.text-white
              .progress
                .progress-bar.bg-secondary{ style: "width: #{@summary[:distance_sum] * 100 / @summary[:distance_goal]}%;" }

%section.py-5.bg-image-full.landing-image-3
  &nbsp;

%section#how.py-5
  .container
    %h1 How can I join?
    %p
      Sign up with Strava or link your existing user account later. Then, mark your
      carbon neutral activities with the hashtag #CarFreeChallenge in the title and
      we'll automatically tally them towards your goals!
    %p
      You can set goals, update progress, win awards for hitting milestones, and share with friends.
    %p
      You can also use the hashtag #CarFreeChallenge on social media to help spread the message!
    %p.text-center
      = link_to 'SIGN UP HERE!', new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-strava"

